      • expandNode

        public void expandNode()
        Expands the current Category. If there are already children in the node, those children are removed before the category is expanded. Then it adds categoryNodes as children if the category has children categories, otherwise it adds all the components of that category in the model as CategoryNodes.
        Specified by:
